@node history "History"

 
       V1.0 - The first version.
              04/11/92
  
       V1.1 - Fixed close bug.
              11/11/92

       V1.2 - Optimized version (Not released).
              (Stardate 6978.3.5)

              o Now support only KS2.04+ machines.
              o Code optimized.
              o Support now CTRL+C
              o Use Amigaguide format (Docs).
        
       V2.0 - New generation DiaMail.
              (StarDate 7061.4.7)

              o Program name is now DiaMail (No DiaWMail).
              o Using now dlg.library.
   
       V2.1 - Small update.
              (StarDate 7103.2.4)

              o Add GetDevName routine (%PORT no more needed).

       V2.2 - New Year Fix.
              (StarDate 8206.5.0)

              o Code optimized. Unneed code removed.
              o DiaMail is shorter and faster.

       V2.5 - Locale support.
              (StarDate 9511.1.2)
   
              o Added locale support. Default language is english.
              o Added switch -p. Check only private mail.

       V3.0 - Total rewritten version.

              o FIRST! Read featurelist.
              o Removed -p switch.
              o No more locale support. No it is language support.
              o Added possibility to read message.
             
@endnode

